data.Name: Anzu Partners
data.About: Venture capital and private equity firm focused on industrial technologies. Launched second $150M fund in 2019.
data.Tagline: Anzu Partners is a venture capital and private equity firm that invests in breakthrough industrial technologies.

data.Name: Bain Double Impact Fund
data.About: Firm makes buyout and control investments in lower middle market companies in North America. Focus on self-identified mission-oriented companies as well as more traditional businesses that create positive social impact
data.Tagline: It builds great companies that deliver both competitive financial returns.

data.Name: Capricorn Investment Group
data.About: Capricorn Investment Group seeks to deliver extraordinary investment results by leveraging market forces to scale solutions to global problems. The Firm was born from a belief that sustainable investment practices can enhance risk-adjusted returns. Underlying this investment approach is a deep desire to demonstrate the huge investment potential that resides in breakthrough commercial solutions to the world’s most pressing problems. One of the largest mission-aligned investment firms in the world, Capricorn has grown to manage more than $5 billion in multi-asset class portfolios for families, foundations and institutional investors. The firm has offices in New York City and Palo Alto.
data.Tagline: Capricorn Investment Group’s mission is to pursue extraordinary investment results by leveraging market forces to scale solutions to global problems.

data.Name: ClearSky Power & Technology
data.About: Invests in innovative companies providing technology and services to enterprise customers, with a special focus on the power sector. $148M raised in for most recent fund.
data.Tagline: ClearSky is a venture capital/growth equity firm.

data.Name: Demeter
data.About: Demeter is a major player in venture capital and private equity for the energy and ecological transition. We invest from €1m to €30m to support companies at all stages of their development: innovative startups, high growth SMEs and infrastructure projects.

data.Name: Homecoming Capital
data.About: Climate change focused firm investing in early stage ventures and in later stage infrastructure projects. Backed by long-term, private investment capital.
data.Tagline: Using capital to fight climate change

data.Name: Idinvest Partners
data.About: The mission of Idinvest Partners, a European leader in financing small and medium-sized enterprises, is to fund European businesses at various stages of growth. With €8 billion under management, we are able to harness a range of complementary solutions to help businesses grow quickly and provide equity and private debt investment, both directly and via private equity funds.
data.Tagline: The go-to investment firm for European SMEs.

data.Name: Impact Engine
data.Tagline: Impact Engine is a venture capital and private equity firm that invests financial and human capital in early-stage companies.

data.Name: Prossano
data.About: Prossano is an impact investing platform that believes that returns don't have to be sacrificed to create impact. With this premise in mind, Prossano invests in companies that are sustainable (those with a profitable business model that can attract capital to scale and create a large impact) and that look to make an impact ( those producing a product or service that has a positive effect on the planet or society)

data.Name: Queensland Investment Corporation
data.About: Created in 1991 by the Queensland government to serve its long-term investment responsibilities, QIC has grown into a leading long-term specialist manager in alternatives. Focuses on infrastructure, real estate, and private capital. Also specialises in liquid market solutions, providing multi-asset portfolios, liquid alternatives, active fixed interest and tailored overlays for clients. Manages $60B. Suitable for funding a large pipeline of projects.
data.Tagline: QIC's vision, mission and standards of excellence guide their approach to all that they do.

data.Name: Vision Ridge Partners
data.About: More than $1B raised to invested in sustainable real assets. Invests across all real asset sectors, including energy, agriculture, transportation and real estate.
data.Tagline: Vision Ridge Partners, LLC, a clean energy oriented investment firm, is active in renewable energy, green building, future utility business models and advanced transportation.

data.Name: Zouk Capital
data.About: Zouk Capital provides private equity for the digital and sustainable economy.

data.Name: Goldwind Innovation Capital
data.About:
Goldwind Innovation Capital is the corporate venture arm of Goldwind Corp. 

Goldwind Corp is a world-leading wind turbine technology and energy solutions provider. Through the implementation and investment in industry-leading turbine technology, water treatment solutions, and other green energy technological ventures, Goldwind has been hailed as one of China’s most innovative companies. The company now operates on 6 continents, has more than 8,000 employees, and more than 50GW of installed wind capacity. Goldwind is committed with social and environmental responsibility, and create a sustainable tomorrow for future generations.
data.Tagline: Goldwind Innovation Capital is dedicated to engaging with promising companies that can enable a sustainable future.
